hopobject.body: How do I get an outside line? southwood pharmacy old bridge • Create a healthy environment: Make sure your physical environment is supportive of your new lifestyle. Don't keep food in the house that is a problem for you. Make sure you have healthy snacks on hand. Make sure you have a place to walk near your house or workplace. Also, create a healthy social environment. Your behaviors are influenced by the people you surround yourself with. Find ways to spend time with people who value the behaviors that you want to maintain.
